<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.2.3">
<l>naṉmaṇi mēkalai naṅkaimā roṭunāḷ toṟum</l>
<l>poṉmaṇi mēṉi puḻutiyā ṭittiri yāmē</l>
<l>kaṉmaṇi niṉṟatir kāṉata riṭaikkaṉ ṟiṉpiṉ</l>
<l>eṉmaṇi vaṇṇaṉaip pōkkiṉē ṉellēpā vamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To stop him with the gold and sapphire [hued] body</l>
<l rend="indent">from wandering about playing in dust</l>
<l>With girls [adorned] with beautiful jeweled girdles everyday,</l>
<l>I sent my sapphire-hued one after the calves on the forest path</l>
<l rend="indent">that thunders like bells on a mountain.</l>
<l>Alas! What a sin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
